..TEXT:
|miseri mortali~: Cf. Virgil, ^Georg.~ III, 66:
"miseris mortalibus" ("hapless mortals").  |aperse~: The subject
of |aperse~ is ^quella~ (Beatrice), in vs. 3.  See ^apersi~ in
this sense in ^Inf.~ X, 44.
