..TEXT:
|gerarcia~ = ^gerarchia.~  |dee~: "Divinities,"
orders of angels.  The term has been applied to angels before
(^Purg.~ XXXII, 8).  Here it should be noted that the three
names of the ^orders~ are feminine.
